  - dialogueID: Maya Bulan 2 event part 1
    dialogueSteps:
    - sentenceText: Basrul!!
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 04073754593a83042b561d10c04a146c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Oh Pemain ada apa?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku mau bertanya apa kamu pernah mengalami mimpi aneh?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Hem...
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Mimpi aneh ya
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Ya kadang-kadang tapi tergantung mimpi apa?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku bermimpi tapi aku seakan akan di sana itu nyata dan ada seorang
        gadis di sana tapi aku tidak bisa melihatnya
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Wow Wow tunggu dulu sebentar
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Mimpi dunia tapi terasa nyata?, ada seorang gadis?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kamu sehat, kan?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Sehat, kok.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Hem... Kalau gitu cerita nya hanya ada 2 ya itu...
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Dia antara kamu memang waktu itu lagi sangat lelah dan banyak
        pikiran atau ada seseorang yang ingin memberi tahu sesuatu lewat dalam mimpimu
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Walau opsi yang kedua itu blak-blakan sekali.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Ya itu sih tergantung yang merasakan
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Jadi bagaimana terbantu?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    choices:
    - choiceText: Iya terima kasih Basrul
      nextDialogueID: Maya Bulan 2 event part 2
      moodTargetHeroine: 0
      moodChangeAmount: 0
      moneyChange: 0
      endOfMonth: 0
      triggerNormalTransition: 1
