      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kamu datang lagi ke sini, Pemain. Aku jadi senang.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku ingin bertanya, Maya.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kenapa Pemain?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kenapa aku mengantuk lebih cepat dari sebelumnya?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Ya, karena di dunia nyata kamu tidak terlalu lelah, jadi waktumu
        di dunia mimpi akan semakin sebentar.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Hem, kenapa aku merasa kamu tidak asing, ya?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "\"(Menunduk sebentar, lalu tersenyum samar)\"Mungkin karena
        hatimu memanggilku. Atau mungkin\u2026 karena aku memang tidak pernah jauh
        darimu"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Tidak pernah jauh? Maksudmu\u2026 kamu ada di sekitarku?"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Kalau aku bilang \u2018iya\u2019, apa kamu akan percaya?"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku tidak tahu. Rasanya terlalu aneh
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Tidak apa-apa. Aku tidak butuh kamu percaya sekarang. Cukup
        rasakan saja\u2026 bahwa aku di sini bersamamu"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Entah kenapa\u2026 aku merasa tenang saat bicara denganmu"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "\"(Tersenyum hangat, menatap lurus ke matamu)\u201C Itu cukup
        bagiku. Aku ingin menjadi tempatmu kembali\u2026 saat dunia nyata terlalu
        berat"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Kamu terdengar seperti\u2026 seseorang yang sangat dekat denganku"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Mungkin begitu. Atau mungkin, aku hanya cerminan dari perasaan
        yang tidak pernah kamu ungkapkan
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Wah, sepertinya waktumu hampir habis lagi.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Oh tidak, aku mengantuk...
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Jangan dipaksakan. Sudah, tutup saja matamu.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Lain kali kita bermain, ya.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Sampai jumpa lagi Pemain
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ab6979896141a04438b11989a02ed2c3, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    choices:
    - choiceText: Tu...nggu...
      nextDialogueID: Maya Bulan 4 event part 2
      moodTargetHeroine: 0
      moodChangeAmount: 0
      moneyChange: 0
      endOfMonth: 0
      triggerNormalTransition: 1
      normalTransitionText: Saat Pemain menutup matanya, Pemain pun bangun dari tidurnya.
      requiredMoodHeroine: 0
      requiredMoodPercent: 0
      moodInsufficientMessage: 
      loadMiniGameScene: 0
      miniGameSceneName: 
      returnDialogueAfterMiniGame: 
  - dialogueID: Maya Bulan 4 event part 2
    dialogueSteps:
    - sentenceText: '"Ini dunia nyata?"'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: '"Tadi itu lumayan lama"'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: '"Karena aku sudah tahu untuk bisa di sana lebih lama"'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: '"Aku akan coba lagi bulan depan"'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: '"Jadi Penasaran"'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: '"Tapi aku harus menunggu bulan depan."'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    choices:
    - choiceText: '"Jadi tidak sabar"'
      nextDialogueID: Maya Bulan 5
      moodTargetHeroine: 0
      moodChangeAmount: 0
      moneyChange: 20000
      endOfMonth: 1
      triggerNormalTransition: 0
      normalTransitionText: 
      requiredMoodHeroine: 0
      requiredMoodPercent: 0
      moodInsufficientMessage: 
      loadMiniGameScene: 0
      miniGameSceneName: 
      returnDialogueAfterMiniGame: 
  - dialogueID: Maya Bulan 5
    dialogueSteps:
    - sentenceText: '"Seharusnya mimpi kali ini aku bisa bertemu dengannya lagi"'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: '"Karena Hari ini aku lelah sekali"'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: '"Oke, ini dia. Aku datang, Maya."'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    choices:
    - choiceText: '"Tidur"'
      nextDialogueID: Maya Bulan 5 event part 1
      moodTargetHeroine: 0
      moodChangeAmount: 0
      moneyChange: 0
      endOfMonth: 0
      triggerNormalTransition: 1
      normalTransitionText: Saat Pemain tertidur dan dia pun berhasil ke dunia mimpi
        yang sama
      requiredMoodHeroine: 0
      requiredMoodPercent: 0
      moodInsufficientMessage: 
      loadMiniGameScene: 0
      miniGameSceneName: 
      returnDialogueAfterMiniGame: 
  - dialogueID: Maya Bulan 5 event part 1
    dialogueSteps:
    - sentenceText: "\u2026ini\u2026"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1d2b21d30705d6641b3bf4d848c6d105, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Dunia mimpi\u2026?"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1d2b21d30705d6641b3bf4d848c6d105, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: '"(Suara langka pelan dari belakang)"'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1d2b21d30705d6641b3bf4d848c6d105, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Kamu akhirnya datang juga\u2026"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1d2b21d30705d6641b3bf4d848c6d105, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Maya\u2026"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1d2b21d30705d6641b3bf4d848c6d105, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "\"(Mendekat perlahan)\"Aku sudah menunggu\u2026"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: Maya Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1d2b21d30705d6641b3bf4d848c6d105, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Di sini?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1d2b21d30705d6641b3bf4d848c6d105, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: 
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 6decb72dfd61e78478bd785d744539fd, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 39ff1e4ce01696a4a8f2234729f6af6b, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: 
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3f80d3a81c0568841837555e2cbbdb8c, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bf1cd5e2fea9f0841b93aabe4e474417, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kamu yang siapkan semua ini?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bf1cd5e2fea9f0841b93aabe4e474417, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    choices:
    - choiceText: Wow...
      nextDialogueID: Maya Bulan 5 event part 2
      moodTargetHeroine: 0
      moodChangeAmount: 0
      moneyChange: 0
      endOfMonth: 0
      triggerNormalTransition: 1
      normalTransitionText: Pemain terkejut karena pemandangannya sangat menenangkan.
      requiredMoodHeroine: 0
      requiredMoodPercent: 0
      moodInsufficientMessage: 
      loadMiniGameScene: 0
      miniGameSceneName: 
      returnDialogueAfterMiniGame: 
  - dialogueID: Maya Bulan 5 event part 2
    dialogueSteps:
    - sentenceText: Ini sangat menenangkan
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b282040174449974492f7962b398255c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: 
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 4a05504c981906943a0dcdb9db9747ad, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 22603e97d9510e0488e30709773d87b0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Iya iya...
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 22603e97d9510e0488e30709773d87b0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: 
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 5fb4ea1336542844b84a86a54640f5b5, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a307f96516c02b942b0a102580770ec7, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: 
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 220f4fd54dcabd14695e986f3c4fc05b, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Maya
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ffef7d8ab1d787344993d1bc1a2cb959, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    choices:
    - choiceText: Terima kasih, Maya.
      nextDialogueID: Maya Bulan 5 event part 3
      moodTargetHeroine: 0
      moodChangeAmount: 0
      moneyChange: 0
      endOfMonth: 0
      triggerNormalTransition: 1
      normalTransitionText: Pemain pun menikmati pikniknya bersama Maya dan tanpa
        sadar saking nyamannya Pemain pun tertidur dan bangun di dunianya
      requiredMoodHeroine: 0
      requiredMoodPercent: 0
      moodInsufficientMessage: 
      loadMiniGameScene: 0
      miniGameSceneName: 
      returnDialogueAfterMiniGame: 
  - dialogueID: Maya Bulan 5 event part 3
    dialogueSteps:
    - sentenceText: '"Kenapa aku tiba-tiba mengeluarkan air mata?"'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: '"Rasa yang hangat ini, aku merasa aku ingin tahu lebih banyak
        lagi tentang nya"'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: '"Tetapi kita memiliki jalan waktu yang berbeda"'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    choices:
    - choiceText: Aku harap aku bisa bersamanya lebih lama.
      nextDialogueID: Tamat
      moodTargetHeroine: 0
      moodChangeAmount: 0
      moneyChange: 0
      endOfMonth: 0
      triggerNormalTransition: 0
      normalTransitionText: 
      requiredMoodHeroine: 0
      requiredMoodPercent: 0
      moodInsufficientMessage: 
      loadMiniGameScene: 1
      miniGameSceneName: Ending
      returnDialogueAfterMiniGame: 
  - dialogueID: Miyu 1
    dialogueSteps:
    - sentenceText: Jadi ini perpustakaannya.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku penasaran ada buku apa saja di sini.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: ...
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Sepertinya ini menarik.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: '"Buku jatuh?!!"'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3c6431efd5b004343934cb374f1fee1b, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Ah, maaf! Ini bukumu, kan?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3c6431efd5b004343934cb374f1fee1b, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Ah\u2026 iya. Terima kasih\u2026"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 97e5c4ce6fa43614eaa0609b135edffc, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Banyak sekali bukumu. Kau suka membaca?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Sedikit. Aku hanya\u2026 lebih nyaman bersama halaman buku daripada
        keramaian."
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: cbca4009ab612c9489df3d594a8a06e6, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Mungkin\u2026 tapi cerita tak pernah berteriak, tak pernah menilai."
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9b0668b930d4a2c42890682cc479ef5d, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku juga suka buku, terutama yang tenang.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Be...benarkah? Kau terlihat seperti orang yang senang berbicara.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: feef4df58d87ac842a42860529def938, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kadang diam pun bisa jadi percakapan, kan?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Kau bicara dengan cara yang aneh ya. Tapi\u2026 tidak buruk."
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 39d59a1536a9b064d91a43c42c463cf8, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
