      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kenapa kamu, Pemain?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Haha...Kau seperti dikejar setan
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku buru-buru masuk kelas, jadi aku lari.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kenapa buru-buru?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Oh iya, kamu anak baru, jadi belum tahu, ya.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Maaf, ini kesalahanku.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Memangnya kenapa?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Bukannya wajar kalau habis istirahat itu harus buru-buru ke kelas?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Uwah... kamu sebelumnya sekolah di mana?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Di sekolah ini jam istirahat memang lama 40 menitan mungkin atau
        lebih
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Walaupun di jadwal kita istirahat hanya 30 menit, sebenarnya
        guru akan masuk 10 menit lebih telat atau mungkin lebih.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Jadi, lain kali kamu tidak perlu buru-buru.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Basrul
      activeCharacterKeys: Basrul Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Harusnya kamu bilang dari awal.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku bahkan tadi tidak dengar namanya saking buru-buru nya
