  - dialogueID: Miiyu Bulan 3 event part 2
    dialogueSteps:
    - sentenceText: Jadi bagaimana kemarin apa ada kendala Miyu?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku masih tidak percaya kalau aku mendapatkan nilai sempurna
        kemarin
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa close up
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Ini berkat kamu Pemain
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa close up
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Ini bukan berkat aku saja tapi berkat kita
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kalau bukan kamu membacakan nya dengan teliti mungkin aku akan
        ragu untuk mengerjakan nya
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Hehe...
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa close up
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku jadi senang bisa mengerjakan pr bersama
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kapan kapan kita mengerjakan tugas bersama lagi boleh kan?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa1f6d4654b77654aaff24713c7893d6, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
