  - dialogueID: Yumi Bulan 2 event 1 part 4
    dialogueSteps:
    - sentenceText: Kamu makan sambil baca ya?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Hah? J-jangan ganggu aku! \u2026Tapi, kalau kamu mau ngobrol
        soal tugas kemarin\u2026 ya, boleh lah."
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Haha, ternyata kamu perhatian juga.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Ja-jangan salah paham! Aku cuma tidak mau kamu dapat nilai jelek
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Iya, iya. Tapi kamu serius sekali sih tiap hari
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kalau tidak serius, terus mau gagal? tidak semua orang santai
        kayak kamu.
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Tapi tetap nemenin aku makan juga kan?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Itu cuma kebetulan! Aku duduk di sini karena\u2026 karena tempat
        lain penuh!"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Padahal kursi sebelah sana kosong tuh
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "I-itu\u2026 aku sudah nyaman di sini, Oke? Jangan banyak tanya!,
        Hump..."
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Close Up
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Hehe, baiklah. Kamu lagi baca apa emangnya?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Catatan matematika. Kamu pasti tidak ngerti
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Enak saja. Sini aku lihat
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Jangan dekat-dekat! \u2026Eh, nanti makanannya jatuh!"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f55b01f803d771548901bb361fe3bb04, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    choices:
    - choiceText: Tenang saja, aku cuma mau belajar kok. Ajari aku dong.
      nextDialogueID: Yumi Bulan 3
      moodTargetHeroine: 2
      moodChangeAmount: 2
      moneyChange: 20000
      endOfMonth: 1
      triggerNormalTransition: 0
      normalTransitionText: 
